{"tid":855263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離有條八婆","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:26:57.000Z","uid":213686,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"167f7648ac1a030cafafe9245d0fa52dd89969f4","tid":855263,"uid":213686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"話説尋日坐巴士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見有部手提電話插咗喺椅與椅之間<br />\n正常會以為係隔離果個跌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問部電話係咪佢嘅<br />\n粒聲唔出就放咗入手袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢一刻都知唔多妥<br />\n不過我又冇理咁多<br />\n諗住只係廢老冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後精彩啦<br />\n轉頭有個後生仔 <br />\n急急腳由樓下走返過來 話&lsquo;<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">頭先跌咗部電話你地有冇見到？</span></span>&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條八婆就扮晒野 施施然手袋拎返出來<br />\n仲死撐話啱啱想拎落去比司機<br />\ndklm一定信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gDqZew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gDqZew.jpg&h=86dae82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1956cf4e0e4587ce8b0fac807c0d9d46f48a4af9","tid":855263,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ab455a483058fe3bb39a6dcf4131ec6dc6edf961","tid":855263,"uid":146434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"個八婆肯交返出黎比個後生仔都算係回頭是岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過搭巴士就落車個陣<br />\n發現跌咗部8plus<br />\n但明明隻錶仲連緊部iphone<br />\n我倒晒成個書包既野出黎都搵唔到<br />\n唯有問下坐我隔離買咗好多袋菜既師奶<br />\n佢冇出聲 落左下層落車<br />\n隻錶就disconnect了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6a09cdf44f0e9aa8303dec13d9a163f38c9e69","